The weakening of the ruble is long-term, and paired with the euro, and paired with the dollar.
The long-term forecast assumed this mark, - says Anna Bodrova, senior analyst at Alpari.
Everything related to Ukraine will be reflected in the courses in one way or another.
As long as this continues, investors will react.
Today, rumors about the invasion of troops are not confirmed on either side, but the market turned out to be very emotional.
All the talk that he was resistant to such news, yesterday was crossed out.
The week, according to forecasts of the specialist, will close around these levels - 36.90 and 37.05 rubles per dollar.
The tax period is over, oil prices are weak, politics, sanctions, the problem of gas transit through Ukraine are all links in one chain.
The acceleration of inflation is also predicted: from 5 to 10% will be added to the current prices for the autumn.
